body:
ci.tensorflow.org is not down. We have deprecated it. Any nightly builds you need can be found at the tf-nightly or tf-nightly-gpu.

Additionally I've just merged the [latest version change](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/commit/d2af5d50b6255c4bc76b9e9fc516a0aa027efe6d). Can you try again with the latest r1.10 branch?
